works.complaint:
When I type in my full name or my company s name in  
Google search engine. I get these URLs defamatory links. These links are  
accusing me and my company of defamatory, unfounded and incorrect  
allegations.
When I click these links to open up and to read more about these  
allegations the organization of the URLs don’t open or the organization  
doesn’t exist anymore.
  Can you please remove these URLs for they are defamatory and are  
portraying misleading and incorrect information about me and my company to  
the public?
In Australian and especially in the state of New South Wales, it is illegal  
to publish any defamatory, incorrect and misleading statements on the  
internet.
  http://www.legislation.nsw.gov.au/
